类 CopyOnWriteLinkedHashMap<K,​V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.modelmapper.internal.util.CopyOnWriteLinkedHashMap<K,​V>
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.util.Map<K,​V>
    public class CopyOnWriteLinkedHashMap<K,​V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Map<K,​V>
    A thread-safe LinkedHashMap which creates a copy of the underlying map on write operations.

    Read operations, including iteration, do not interfere with writes since the underlying map is never modified.
